[b]Info[/b]: Server Name: Pbscape Server based off of: Deltascape Owners: Pblord7.
[b]Goals[/b]: -Very stable server -Have a decent player average -Great Economy -Fun to play server -Very few glitches

Dragon Claws Spec Crossbow Emote AGS Spec BGS Spec ZGS Spec SGS Spec Overloads Rocktails Karil's Bow on NPC's Staff Of Light Magic in PVP/NPCS(while attacking) Fix magic (can cast on any levels) Dragon Bow Glitch Fix Overload Effect Black Mask (Works just like Rune scape and help's a lot during Slayer Tasks.) PVP Drops DFS Effect DDS Glitch Fix Bank Pins X2 XP System for Double EXP Weekends You attack NPC's before they attack you Elemental Staff's don't use runes "Magic Staff" doesn't use runes Rocktail Effect Torva Effect (for when Torva is added) DDS Hits twice at the same time Combination Runes
